name: Dora the Explorer: Carnival 2 - Boardwalk Adventure
D.M. Dinwiddie, Physician-in-Training
description:
Developed by Health Media Lab with grants from the National Institutes of Health, D.M. DINWIDDIE, PHYSICIAN-IN-TRAINING teaches children to identify and treat 12 common medical conditions: burns, choking, insect bites and stings, bumps and bruises, cuts and bleeding, sunburn, sprains and broken bones, food poisoning, common cold, influenza, tonsillitis, and appendicitis. Kids play as D.M. Dinwiddie, a 12-year old girl or boy (player's choice) who is earning a Medical Arts Achievement Badge. Through a series of interactive adventures, D.M. finds injured characters in her virtual neighborhood, including her little brother who has an insect bite.

By looking at and talking with the injured characters, and then using a special MedLab (an onscreen database that serves as a reference and diagnostic guide) and her first-aid kit, D.M. is able to diagnose and treat the hurt people.

name: Parthian Strike
description: Decades after the war with the machines, mankind has fallen into underground shelters to escape nuclear radiation. However, they are destroyed one by one by machine soldiers walking on the ground. The people challenge their last battle with humanoid weapons that were once used in the Great War.

name: Sidestep Legends
description: Practise your sidestep skills as you dodge spells coming at you from all directions. Level up and choose from a variety of upgrades and new abilities to increase your chances of survival in this moba inspired rogue-lite. Unlock new characters and explore different skill combinations each round.

name: Seekers of Tokane
description: Embark on a thrilling journey through diverse landscapes, each brimming with wondrous creatures known as Nefties. These captivating beings are yours to collect, train, and trade as you navigate and battle your way through the universe of Aurory.

name: Play Chess: Deep Fritz - Grandmaster Deluxe
Non Fingo
description: VR spaceship crew simulator with realistic physics and extensive mod support.

name: The Little Spirit of the East
description: The Little Spirit of the East is a mystery adventure game set in a legendary village.

name: Dark Hermetic Order
description: A cancelled first person action adventure game planned as a sequel to Azrael's Tear. Players would take the role of a secret agent with magic powers, who infiltrates a strange cult to eliminate their leaders.

name: Mysteries In Paradise
description: 10 complete casual games from award-winning developer YoudaGames. Puzzles, adventures, mysteries and simulations of all sorts, including all the major casual games elements: mystery, adventure, hidden object, strategy, puzzle, fantasy, simulation, time & resource management, and even card games.

name: Mystery Trackers: The Void & Shiver: Vanishing Hitchhiker
description: This is a collection of two hidden-object games in which players search for human characters that have mysteriously gone missing. Players solve puzzles and search through screens filled with jumbled objects to uncover clues and advance the storylines

name: Private Dick: Lipstick & Lies
description:
Private Investigator Sam Steele is in a rut. His clients have dried up, his useless secretary is (still) waiting to be paid, and his ex-girlfriend has broken the sanctity of his favourite bar.

It's almost a relief when a case walks through the door. Almost. A missing dog, an unrequited debt and a suspicious kidnapping all come to a head in a dingy motel out of town.

Mystery and comedy combine in this mature and complex story.

name: Flame Tale
description: Flame Tale is a 2D fantasy platform game. Ride the wind, block the rain.

name: Disney's Activity Center: Winnie the Pooh
Disney's Winnie the Pooh & Tigger Too: Animated Storybook
description: Animated StoryBook: Winnie the Pooh and Tigger Too is a PC video game released on April 30, 1999. This Disney's Winnie the Pooh adventure is presented in the form of a colourful storybook. Each page in the story is presented on screen with text and a full-colour interactive picture

name: Def Jam Fight for NY Mobile
Dark Tales: Edgar Allan Poe's Murders in the Rue Morgue - Collector's Edition
Deal or No Deal: Secret Vault Games
Sherlock Holmes: The Hound of the Baskervilles - Collector's Edition
Shrek 2 Activity Center: Twisted Fairy Tale Fun
Operation: Hostage Rescue - Close Quarters Combat
Yu Yu Hakusho: Dark Martial Arts Club

Menhera Kanojo to Boku: Uwaki shitara Jinsei Shuuryou yo
Oscar the Balloonist: Discovers the Farm
Oscar the Ballonist flies into the Mountains
Oscar the Ballonist & The Secrets of the Forest
Oscar the Balloonist: Drops Into the Country Side
Oscar the Balloonist: My Creative Workshop
Penny Dreadfuls: Sweeney Todd - Premium Edition
Space Shuttle Mission Simulator: The Collector's Edition
Roadsters '98
description: Roadsters '98 is pretty much a complete racing game that was given the red light.

name: Inertia: Redux
description: Inertia: Redux is a first-person action platformer with free-run inspired movement mechanics. Through use of the fluid movement set within the game and the dynamic level elements, players have the simple aim of getting from point A to point B.

name: Tango Race: Nou Training Kotoba Game
Curse of the Pharaoh: Napoleon's Secret
Firefighter: Car Fire Truck Sim Driving 2022 Simulator
description: In the game Firefighter: Car Fire Truck Sim Driving 2022 Simulator, you have to try on the role of a real fire brigade worker in a large American city.

name: Inertia: Redux
description: Inertia: Redux is a first-person action platformer with free-run inspired movement mechanics. Through use of the fluid movement set within the game and the dynamic level elements, players have the simple aim of getting from point A to point B.

name: Breakyo
description: Classic Brick-Breaking game with a slight fusion which completely alters the fundamental gameplay.

name: Crystal Compulsion
description: Crystal Compulsion is a fast, deep, and unique deckbuilding roguelike. Craft a killer deck by converting, devouring, or killing all that stand in your way. Find the synergies between the current 150+ cards, climb the 12 ascension levels, and battle the cute but deadly animal creatures.

name: Daybreaker VR
description: Scavenge loot to survive in this zombie infested post-apocalyptic sandbox VR shooter. Piece together your own guns from the loot you find, or go toe-to-toe with nothing more than a sharpened stick.

name: Demons and Altar
description: Demons and Altar is a challenging strategy game. Players will carry out an expedition in the magical world. On the way, players can choose their own route, recruit their own heroes, defeat the emerging enemies, and finally defeat the great demon king.

name: Doom & Destiny Worlds: Randomicity
description: Randomize the islands disposition with the new game mod and buy 3 houses at a reasonable price!

name: Kentor and also Bloby in: Part 1 - The Krookening
description: Join Kentor and also Bloby on a colorful quest to catch Krooktor and save their invention!

name: Master of the Tattooverse
description: Master of the Tattooverse is a story-driven tattoo game that allows you to create and share art pieces in a wacky universe. Enjoy the freedom of creating your own tattoos for extraordinary clients. Use templates or just do it freehand, satisfy your customers and expand your own tattoo portfolio.

name: Panelki: Delivery
description: Tired of being a janitor? Now you can become a delivery man! A big heavy bag instead of shovels, an attractive smell from it and the same goal to save up for a ticket to start a new life (again?).

name: Puzzle Me
description: The ultimate VR jigsaw puzzle solving experience. Designed from the ground up for VR. With simple, intuitive controls and a wide range of unique difficulty options it can be enjoyed by players who wouldn't call themselves jigsaws fans as well as providing a mind bending challenge to expert solvers!

name: Roxy Raccoon's Pinball Panic: Wacky West
description: 3 Brand New Tables with online leaderboards and unlockable cosmetics! Wild Western themed tables with a 50's and 60's style pinball inspiration.

name: Super Jigsaw Puzzle: Generations - Ice Creams
Valand
description: Valand is a Viking Age city builder. With your own strength you have to rebuild the whole settlement and bring it to prosperity.

name: Train Sim World 2: Island Line 2022 - BR Class 484 EMU
description: Experience a unique marvel of rail innovation, an Underground veteran turned Solent explorer. Modern-day Isle of Wight duties await with Rivet Games’ Island Line 2022: BR Class 484 for Train Sim World 2!

name: The Mean Greens: Plastic Warfare - Vampiro
description: Lucha Libre icon, Guardian Angel, a man of many talents, sinks his teeth into a new role as he becomes part of the plastic-melting team of "The Mean Greens - Plastic Warfare".

name: Katz Play
description: Katz is a cooperative multiplayer game with thieving cats, where you will dock with friends with multiple levels full of traps and obstacles. The objective: to accumulate richness to become a stylish cat.

name: Crystalize! 2: Quest for the Jewel Crown
Matchbox Caterpillar Construction Zone 2: Gold Mining
Sphera: The Inner Journey
description: Join Tess, a lonely young girl, on a perilous journey into a world born from her imagination in Sphera, a new hidden object adventure from Sandlot Games! Teased relentlessly by her older brother for her quirks and oversized glasses, Tess longs to escape her isolated life. Her chance arrives when she discovers a mysterious marble that transports her to a bizarre realm ruled by a kind walrus-like creature named Zuchary. However, when Zuchary's adopted son, Jacob, betrays him, he turns to Tess for help. In return, she will be given the chance to return home. Aid Tess in embracing her true destiny as a warrior princess in Sphera!

name: SpongeBob SquarePants and the Nicktoons Gravjet Racing
description: SpongeBob SquarePants and the Nicktoons Gravjet Racing was a racing game planned for release in 2009 featuring characters from SpongeBob SquarePants, Barnyard, Ren And Stimpy, Fanboy And Chum Chum, My Life As A Teenage Robot, The Mighty B and possibly more. Before its cancellation, the ESRB rated the game and gave it an E rating along with stating that it was intended to be released for the Xbox 360 and PC. The name of the developers and publisher however have not been revealed.

name: Spy Fox Dry: Cereal and Cheese Chase - Activity Game
Sticky Balls
description:
Over 1.3 million games of Sticky Balls have been played! Sticky Balls is the most addictive game on the app store right now. The simple gameplay and sleek look combine with a deceptively difficult gameplay that will have you yelling at your phone while rushing to start your next game!
You will be lulled by the cheery music into bouncing around this minimal world. But along the way you will have to avoid the sticky balls. The more balls that stick to you, the harder it is to fit through the levels. Luckily there are helpful diamonds throughout the game that help remove the balls that latched on. See how high you can go with Sticky Balls!

name: Mir M
description:
MMORPG and Sequel to MIR4 (2021), In the world of MIR M, strength is not the only factor in measuring one's growth.

You can walk the path of the hero, ruling over the battlefield with overwhelming power. Or, you can walk the path of the master, gathering, mining, and fishing to reach the highest level.

Whichever path of growth you choose is completely up to you. The results of the choice you make will be recognized by all as meaningful.

name: Story Play
description: Your choices change the ending! Become the protagonist of the story and make the story with your own choices.

name: Boku no Bottakuri Bar 3: Sekai shinshutsu-hen
Runelords
description: Runelords is a cancelled RPG that was in development in 1999 / 2000 by Saffire and it would have been published by Kemco for the GameBoy Color. The game was based on the fantasy book series with the same name, created by David Farland.

name: Saddle Up with Pippa Funnell Olympic Medalist
Sailboat Championship
description: We have the pleasure to invite you to participate in a sea racing experience like never before! It does not matter if you are a novice or adept sailor, participate in thrilling regattas and fast paced races against computer-controlled opponents, compete online with players from all over the world, upgrade and unlock new boats, complete amazing and action-filled courses and collect all in-game trophies and gold awards! Become the ultimate master of Sailboat Championship - the only true and addicting sailing simulation with unique gameplay for your device.

name: Shangri La 2: The Valley of Words
Five Nights at Candy's 4
description: Five Nights at Candy's 4 is a upcoming fourth installment of the Five Nights at Candy's series developed by Emil Macko. Five Nights at Candy's 4 will be the fourth and last game of the Five Nights at Candy's series. Forgotten Candy is confirmed to be the main antagonist of the game.

name: Age of Dynasties: Pharaoh
description: A turn-based strategy set in ancient Egypt.

name: Space Resistance
description: Space Resistance is a classic shoot'em-up style game with a rogue-like level system. The aim is to defeat as many enemy ships as possible and get the highest score by surviving as long as possible!

name: Silent Hunter: Commander's Edition
description: Silent Hunter Commander's Edition is the compilation of the original Silent Hunter and patrol disks (expansion packs) 1, 2, and 3. Patrol disk 3 adds two more patrol zones, Aleutian Islands and Java Sea. Fifteen additional historical scenarios are included.

name: Scary Mansion Horror House HD
description: Welcome to your new mansion, on the Scary Mansion: Horror House 3D!

name: Cityscape Sprint
description: Use your momentum in this arcade style platformer to conquer each stage and climb the leaderboards. Enjoy 2-4 hours of tight gameplay in bright, cheerful levels - easy to beat but impossible to perfect.

name: Roots in the Sky: The Hand of Glory 2
description: After five years in hiding, former Miami detective Lazarus “Lars” Bundy is swept up in another globe-trotting supernatural mystery whose origins trace back to a legend about the creation of Earth itself.

name: The Mystery of William Moore
description: Put on your detective hat, and get ready for the mystery of a lifetime. Embark on a plot-driven, walking simulator-puzzle video game with an amazing plot and surprise ending.

name: Avici
description: Use the daytime to search for treasures, trade with hermits, and investigate the strange experiences of former expedition members; Or with limited oxygen and lighting equipment, dive deep into the endless darkness of the seabed, escape the threat of unknown creatures, and seek powerful technology.

name: Climate State
description: The Climate State application offers a convenient way to browse climate science topics, videos about climate change, and related news.

name: Geronimo
description: Geronimo is an immersive, tactical CQB shooter built for Virtual Reality that depicts a modern-day world in which Special Forces operators are called to implement unconventional operations as members of elite teams. Engage in the most realistic combat experience available. "Who Dares, Wins"

name: Last of Ark
description: A roguelike deckbuilding tactics game that combines elements from 'Monster Train' and 'Into the Breach'.The player needs to establish organization in a destroyed world, defend against enemy attacks, and restore order.

name: Containerphobia
description: The protagonist wakes up inside a container with a lamp, a flashlight and a video surveillance point. Outside is full of other containers. Darkness all around, walls visible in the distance. We need to get out of this weird place! Somewhere in the darkness, something...

name: Gravity Flux
description: A 2D local multiplayer shooter featuring robots, where the gravity randomly changes. Up to 8 players.

name: Loop Grow
description: Loop Grow is an Psychological Horror based in a layer based growing loop of different environments and mysteries.

name: Canis Major
description: When good dogs die, they don't stop being man's best friend. You play as Comet: a recently deceased sheepdog tasked with guarding his family in the spiritual realm of dreams. Set in Wales during the aftermath of World War II, we find out just how important it is to have a best friend in Heaven.

name: Miyeon-si Simyulleiteo: Misonyeo Geimui Juingongeul Jojonghaneun Geim
Limited Lifetime Corp
description: Lead your LLC to its inevitable destruction in this day by day management sim. Harvest resources, make a profit, expand your Corp. But be careful; from the local fauna to the Syndicate, no one wants you to succeed.

name: Lunatic
description: Neighbors reported a scream from a man's apartment next door. They claim that different women have been coming in and out of the house lately. You're a police officer and it's your duty to check it out.

name: Doodle Drive
description: DoodleDrive is a 2d creative driving / puzzle / physics game. Doodle roads and shapes and unleash your driving skills on the path you have crafted to reach the Finish line.

name: Minimal Bubble Pop
description: Keep your score high with bubble management skills.

name: Star Boss
description: Make robots and spaceships,explore the space,fight with aliens.

name: Island Games
description: Island games - You life. The game includes several game modes that are suitable for competition with other people or bots. You can also relax and communicate with other players on the island.

name: VR Jurassic island roller coaster
description: This is a VR adventure game where players will drive a roller coaster from a first-person perspective to experience the scenery of two different worlds.

name: VR Dinosaur Fight
description: This is a casual dinosaur fighting game. Players can walk freely on the map, view prehistoric islands and watch dinosaurs up close. Players can also choose their favorite dinosaurs and fight with enemy dinosaurs in the arena to win. , to unlock new dinosaurs.

name: Binary
description: Binary is a game that requires players to mix the ability to solve puzzles and effectively platform. It is about Bit, a piece of computer data, trying to find his fellow bits who got lost in a data transfer.

name: Meta Sudoku
description: Meta Sudoku is a minimalist game, fresh interface and quiet music is very suitable for relaxation, reduce fatigue, give you the most comfortable experience.

name: Project Echoes
description: Save the once peaceful land in Project Echoes. Explore an interconnected world overrun by evil ghostly apparitions. Slash and shoot your enemies as two heroes each with their own unique abilities in this action adventure platformer.

name: Blobble Wars 2
description: Mouse-based physics strategy game. Take the other team's towers before they can take yours! Features 50 unique levels and four difficulty modes.

name: Paresis
description: Paresis is a challenging horror experience like no other. This will test your ability to listen, use logic and deductive reasoning, and to divine critical noises that grant important information that could be life or death. Just a house in the middle of nowhere...what lies beyond?

name: Spooky Milk Life
description: Come on to the 'Spooky Milk Life', Explore and solve the mystery of Mid Night Falls with full of sexy characters and erotic situations. Procedural dungeon and Turn-based battle are waiting.

name: Super Hentai Racers
description: Cute but challenging race action gameplay. Win races to upgrade your vehicle to become the top racer.

name: Bokura no Keshigomu Otoshi Shin Gakki
description: Play more! Hit it! Poke it off! The new school year begins with our Eraser Droppers! Battle anytime, anywhere!

name: Nobunaga no Yabou: Oretachi no Sengoku
description:
When Sengoku, number of powerful era.
Invest only in "real-time large-scale battle" of decisive, let's aim to expand its own power!

name: Blocks
description: Slide the orange block off the board by sliding the other blocks out of its way. The horizontal blocks only move left and right, while the vertical blocks slide up and down. Solving the puzzles can be very tricky, but don't worry, the first ones are easy and will get you going quickly.

name: Astro Command Scramble Retro!
description: This is an accurate conversion from that retro vintage classic from the early 1980's brought forward to the 21st Century. Scramble by Grandstand and Astro Command by Epoch, Radio Shack and many other companies in the 80's are all the same game but in a different shell with a different name.

name: Snowball Fall Down
description: Maneuver Mr Snowball down the platforms quick enough so that you don't smash into the icicles!

name: Lost in the Open
description: Lost In The Open is an atmospheric turn-based tactical game set in a procedurally generated low-fantasy world. As the target of an assassination attempt, you must fight tooth and nail to escape through the forests of Wailon while repenting for your past crimes as king.

name: Helicopter Gunship DEX
description: Helicopter Gunship DEX aims to replicate the brilliance of 90s helicopter simulators using modern technology. Employ realistic helicopter tactics during missions generated by a sophisticated random mission generator giving you an almost unlimited amount of re-playability.

name: Pawn Shop Simulator
description: Run your pawn shop in the 50's , buy from customers for low price and resell for higher one , survive and upgrade your shop to maximize your income !

name: Brave Heroes
description: Kill thousands of creatures and try to complete four seasons. Brave Heroes is a casual action rogue-lite game about using both environment and magical powers to survive against thousands of creatures that only aim to kill you.

name: Pindeavor
description: Pindeavor takes overhead action-RPG style mechanics and themes them along pinball-like powers. Bump, bounce, roll, and reflect obstacles as you make your way through 9 dungeons, facing off against enemies, bosses, and lots of balls and bricks.

name: Grand Gate
description: Summon your Towers. Defend yourself from the Gateborn, sworn enemies of humanity. Discover the secrets of the Grand Gate in this Tower Defense RPG game.

name: Bow-Bots
description: Bow-Bots Is a VR Multiplayer Bow and Arrow Shooter.

name: Tainted Gun
description: Travel the universe as a hired gun and explore strange planets in this fast-paced roguelite action platformer. Can you find a cure against the taint before your time runs out?

name: Space Bunny Explorers
description: After crashing on a planet in search of a new adventure, you decide to support an exploration team that gets attacked by robots and wild animals and help them unravel the mysteries of the planet named Kepler-452c.

name: Once Upon a Time in Morocco
description: Explore the ancient and mysterious dreamland of “Once Upon A Time In Morocco”, traveling through the golden sands, discovering their secrets and their ruins, and collecting the Lost Tablets of Self Acceptance.

name: Family Chess: Deluxe Edition
description: Pick your favorite Choose one of the heroes and challenge other players in this family-friendly version of Chess.

name: Luberman and the Legend of Animals Warriors
description: Journey through we landscapes as the adventure will take you to the final part of the game where you will be challenged and tested in a dramatic boss fight. It will take a lot of courage and effort to prove yourself worthy. As a Lumberman, your mission w…

name: Shiro: Midori
description:
Midori, sequel to the award-winning puzzle game Shiro, tells the wondrous story of priest Yoshida. Together, you leave home and bring back hope to the people of Kyoto.

Travel through dark forests to invite the ancient gods, the Kami-sama, to Yoshida’s shrine. Solve challenging, handmade puzzles by placing emptiness in between maple trees to the Kami-sama.

Animal messengers of the gods will cross your way and offer their help. Learn Japanese words from them and whisper with the wind.

name: Roll Turtle
description: Roll Turtle is an easy to play but challenging, action driven puzzle platformer That embarks you on an exciting rolling journey. Help Daddy Turtle to save his baby in 5 fantastic worlds! That's Rolling!

name: Omber
description:
Omber is an immersive, first-person, role-playing game.The Wizard Somes has captured the Princess Kroma and keeps her prisoner in the Omber, an alternate dimension. He uses her magical powers to enslave the local villagers to work in his mines.
It's your mission to kill Somes, free the villagers and free the Princess. There are resistance fighters who will help you. You'll have Root, a wise Ent to adventure at your side.
Move within a beautiful, 3d world with appeal and challenges for Adventurers of all ages.
Old-school atmosphere.
Easy controls.
Multiple side quests in addition to your main missions.
Level up by battling your foes.
Earn reputation points by doing good deeds.
Find Sparkles of Happiness to fatten your purse.
Mine, create potions, weave, make shoes, forge weapons and more.

name: Popgoes Finale
description:
After Simon's successful domination of The Popgoes Pizzeria, a mangled Sec-Strings makes one last effort to communicate with WeaselWare. After hours of silence, and with only a few days of power left, a sign of life finally appears...
Fritz Glade is alive.

In POPGOES Finale, a dying Fritz takes a dying Strings through a selection of memories from his mysterious and misfortunate past, adding to and concluding the story of the POPGOES series.

Traverse through beautiful pixel art environments with a brand new chiptune soundtrack. This is not a horror game! There are no jumpscares, no dying... in fact, there is no losing at all. Just walk around and take the story in.

name: Jane & John
description: A visual novel with several built-in minigames featuring a different kind of erotic story between Jane and John.

name: Particle Hearts
description: Particle Hearts is a 3rd-person adventure game where you explore a world made entirely of particles. Use special abilities to manipulate those particles, solve puzzles, avoid detection, and navigate this sinister and beautiful land.

name: Moonman
description: Moonman is a power of lunar energy created in a laboratory far from Earth. This is a 2D action game in which you run to the real moon while releasing powerful beams with self-inflicted damage and cleaving off the approaching enemies. Aim for the fastest clear while properly managing your energy!

name: Topia
description: Topia is a Time travel, choice based VR adventure game where the future is literally in your hands!

name: Magnetic Bonds
description: Magnetic Bonds is a fusion of the visual novel and turn-based RPG genres inspired by shonen manga where players explore a vast galaxy, befriending characters and building relationships as they progress through the story and take down enemies and bosses.

name: Hide Alone
description: You try to play dangerous hide-and-seek with a doll at home alone. Started out of curiosity, this hide-and-seek game has rules that must be followed or your life will be at risk. Never get caught by them, stay calm and survive to the end.

name: Metro Mover
description: Drive metro trains to move the low poly people of Blueton in this sim-arcade game.

name: Red Fury
description: Fast paced arcade action where you become stronger as you are covered in the blood of your enemies and your own wounds.

name: Axis of Power
description: Stylized characters fight focusing on gameplay mechanics MORE than common input dexterity requirements! A pick up and play arcade-style 3D fighter that will keep you on your toes at all levels!

name: Sich Tactics
description: Sich Tactics is a small turn-based tactics set in Ukrainian mythology world. Take control over a party of Cossacks of different classes in procedurally generated battles, fight with chorts, muscovites and other unholy spirits, complete scenarios or compete with other players in special mode.

name: Eye of the Portal
description: Make your way to the surface in the Action bullet-hell game and embark on a quest to fight your god and break the curse. You are the child of the eye and you must go against your morals to break the curse for all.

name: Galacticorp
description: Galacticorp is a multiplayer incremental trading and crafting sim. Grow your wealth through co-operation or conquest. Navigate Galacticorp's player-driven economy to climb to the top, unlocking new passive and active gameplay mechanics as your prestige grows.

name: Escape Chase Zombie
description: "Escape & Chase Zombie" is action game where you collect spheres on the map while escaping from zombies. zombies use their very smart brains to chase you. Escape from zombies with your instant judgment & selected items!!

name: PlayWith
description: Tired of the old "WASD/ZQSD" key binding ? Want to challenge you with some weird key bindings ?PlayWith is a 2D hardcore platform game where every level have a different key bindingDid you ever jumped with "Y", got to the left with "5" and to the right with "E" ?

name: Farpost 44
description: Farpost 44 is an Action-Adventure taking place in a 44-hour time loop. Unlock multiple story-paths and endings to unravel the mystery of the Farpost 44 catastrophe where each playthrough is based on your choices and actions.

name: Pace Chasers
description: Join the ranks of the Pace Chasers, a league of interdimensional speedsters, as they travel through time and space on a grand tour of races to become the fastest beings in the universe.

name: The Monster Mole
description: An asymmetrical PvP horror survival game where you either try to survive and escape a vicious beast with your teammates, or hunt your prey as the nearly-blind monster that inhabits the surroundings of the fictional town of Dry Lake.

name: Carnival of Gods: Oppression
description: An imprisoned Tyrant God risks to escape thanks to the help of his disciples. In a mission for your Gods and your people travel to his prison, Limbo, a powerful magical place and stop his rising before its too late or your world will be ruined.

name: Scare Train VR
description: Scare Train VR is a Ghost Train in fully immersive Virtual Reality. A six-minute ride through a Creepy abandoned mine, that is far from empty. Please take a seat and Prepare for Suspense and Jump Scares. Are you brave enough to ride the Scare Train?

name: A Webbing Journey
description: A Webbing Journey is a physics-based sandbox game where you play as a cute little spider. Explore a giant house, create crazy web structures, and complete oversized chores in creative and fun ways.

name: Fight For It
description: Turn-based, rogue-like adventure of randomness. Roll lots of dice to test your luck.

name: 8 Days
description: You have 8 days before the final fight. At your current state, you do not stand a chance! Explore this Open World to gain new skills and abilities for the battle. Choose where you go, what you do carefully. You cannot waste time! You have 8 days.

name: SGS Operation Downfall
description: Project Manhattan failed! Operation Downfall, the Allied plan for the invasion of the Japanese home islands is set in motion. Start with Operation Olympic to capture Kyushu, and move on with Coronet, the landing near Tokyo. Force Japan surrender with the largest amphibious operation in history.

name: Summer Road
description: Summer Road is a new RPG based on the concept of playing RPGs more casually. It targets people who are tired of AAA RPGs and want to play in a short time, and want to immerse themselves in nostalgia.

name: Satus
description: Satus - global fantasy strategy, in which you can lead one of the 4 fractions: magicians, dwarfs, dark side, hell virus. Every fraction is unique. Capture all the enemies, arrange the end of the world, build a great empire!

name: Sloth Simulator Almost
description: Sloth Simulator is a round based combat mini game with fun gadgets and action heavy movement skills to unlock. Play as and upgrade your slot! Defeat enemies and unlock different islands as you adventure!

name: Pita-Ten Minigame: Gohan to ka dekimasu
RedNeg 3Stars
description: Doujin bullet hell STG by あうとさいど.

name: Gary Grigsby's World at War: A World Divided
description: Gary Grigsby’s World At War: A World Divided brings you to back to the dawn of the greatest and most terrible war the world has ever seen. Take command in this dynamic, turn-based strategy game of World War II that puts you in the role of some of the most legendary leaders of history. In Gary Grigsby’s World At War: A World Divided, you have complete control over the production, research and military strategy for your side.

name: The Legend of Zelda: Mystical Seed of Wisdom
description: The Legend of Zelda: Mystical Seed of Wisdom is an unreleased game in The Legend of Zelda series that planned to be a released with Mystical Seed of Courage and Mystical Seed of Power. The game was cancelled due to difficulties linking all 3 games together. Some of its elements were integrated into Mystical Seed of Power, which was renamed Oracle of Seasons, while Mystical Seed of Courage became Oracle of Ages.

name: Hexoplanet
description: You take control over a robot civilization that recently achieved self-consciousness and needs to prepare a new planet for their masters, the humans.

name: ExpressLane
description: ExpressLane is a 32 player multiplayer 1st person shooter. You and your friends team up to destroy enemy teams' respawn points, while defending your own. The map is built from randomly-selected floating islands connected by ExpressLanes that players can fly through. Last team standing wins!

name: Code: To Jin Yong
description: Code: To Jin Yong is a tribute to well-known wuxia writer, Jin Yong. The new game is based on the world created in his wuxia novel series.

name: Our Summer Sports
description: Beat the heat with some thrilling summer games! Pass around the Joy-Con controllers and compete with up to four players! From Surfing to Jet Ski and even the Water Slider, there are ten exciting sports to try!

name: Crazy Plane Landing
description: Fly high and try to stick the landing. Will you survive or will you crash?

name: Censored Files
description:
Censored Files is the one and only crime fiction word-puzzle game!
Use your sixth sense to figure out what happened.

name: Box to Box
description: A fun platform puzzle game. 20 levels are waiting for you to challenge. Gamepad

name: Prostitute Simulator
description: Experience the life of an attractive and sensual prostitute and seduce your clients in a city full of policemen, gangsters and cheated women in Japan, where prostitution is prohibited and your life is in danger at every corner.

name: Descension
description: Descension is a Horror themed FPS That features FREE episodic releases, and large open-world environments.

name: Dreamland: Village Life
description: A Reimagined Open-World Game Inspired by Classics. Farming, Fishing, RPG Adventures, Weapons Manufacturing, Mining, Diving, World Exploration, and Making Friends with Cute Villagers!

name: The Horror of Oz
description: The Horror of Oz is a maze runner that has Dorothy returning to a frightening rendition of Oz, where she must peruse through dark and treacherous mazes in search of escape, while being chased by corrupted versions of her dearest friends.

name: Land of Nod
description: Land of Nod is a low-poly art-style sci-fi shooting game. The player will fight against colonial leaders on a far beyond colony planet: The Planet Nod. And explore the secret hidden in this planet and the entire universe.

name: E-Elementals
description: In E-Elementals you will play as E-Elemental 1k7. E-Elementals are advanced bots that are tasked with doing a variety of different tests and trials. Initially the tests seem normal, but 1k7 will quickly learn the truth behind them...

name: Dead Train
description: A zombie survival game that takes place in a post-apocalyptic wasteland. You must manage your food and water carefully because resources are limited. You need to make your way to the end of the railway and back to civilization.

name: OneBit Berzerk
description: Classic arcade Berzerk gameplay for your PlayDate console

name: Delivery Quest
description: Deliver the package and escape the cursed sword.

name: Freeland
description: freeland is an infinite prairie, away from buzz and noise, where you can mentally stay, rest and regain your strength and balance, through nature, solitude, and serenity.

name: I.Rule
description:
I.Rule is a tower-defense fangame based on The Binding of Isaac: Rebirth and Plants vs. Zombies.

It's a roguelite where you fight monsters using babies with different abilities, based on familiars from The Binding of Isaac. Fight bosses, complete various challenges and craft the most effective strategy to win!

name: Tactical Warrior
description: Tactical Warrior is a strategic RPG with fast paced, turn based battles. Battle the men and beasts of the land as you discover new items and strengthen your team of warriors.

name: Rocket Bunnies
description: The debut game from the makers of Ski Safari, and the best space rabbit sim you'll play this year!

name: The Heart of Sourcerer
description: "The Heart of Sourcerer" is a short, comic-style RPG!

name: Tower Defense King
description: Tower Defense game with action and strategy

name: ColorCube
description: A first-person 3D puzzle game. Objects of the same color cannot collide with each other, and you're no exception. But not only you can change the color of yourself, but also you can change the color of other objects with a wand. This game has 43 levels. It takes about an hour to pass.

name: Pacebreaker: An Experiment in AI-Perfected Exercise
description: VR is not just fun exercise. It's the first generation of exercise equipment capable of meaningful live bio-feedback. Pacebreaker is the VR Health Institute's testing ground for research-based next generation exercise in VR, artificial intelligence, and content that can help save lives.

name: Trainz Railroad Simulator 2022: Pro Train - Class 68 ScotRail
description: The Class 68 is a type of mainline mixed traffic diesel-electric locomotive manufactured by Stadler Rail (and previously by Vossloh España) for Direct Rail Services (DRS) in the United Kingdom. This dlc - made by 3DZUG for the Pro Train series, is in the ScotRail livery.

name: Trainz Plus DLC: Pro Train - Class 68 ScotRail
description: The Class 68 is a type of mainline mixed traffic diesel-electric locomotive manufactured by Stadler Rail (and previously by Vossloh España) for Direct Rail Services (DRS) in the United Kingdom. This dlc - made by 3DZUG for the Pro Train series, is in the ScotRail livery.

name: Voidwalkers: The Gates of Hell - Death to the Heretics!
description: Outpost Charlie has finally been breached by the realm of the dead. The entities of The Void have started the process of turning the land into a toxic wasteland. You and your team have been tasked with holding the line until evacuation procedures can be completed.

name: Train Simulator: Long Island Rail Road - New York: Hicksville Route
description: America’s busiest, most historic, and legendary commuter railroad – the Long Island Rail Road – now comes to Train Simulator Classic! A trio of iconic New York City terminals (Penn Station in Manhattan, Atlantic Avenue in Brooklyn, and Long Island City), across “The Island” to Hicksville, New York.

name: Thunderbolt Boxing
description: This is a single-player action street fighting game. During the game, you need to defeat various ambush enemies and boss to obtain the final victory.

name: Interrogation Simulator
description: Inspired by JCS videos and similar Interrogation analysis. Match evidence with statements. Play good cop/bad cop. Make choices. Learn what makes people tick. Unravel the mystery.

name: Aliens vs. Ghosts
description: Use Nukes, Electricity, Freeze Rays, Heat Rays and powerful Minions to defeat all the Ghosts in this wave-based first person shooter! Only Ghosts stand in the way of your invasion of Earth.

name: Jelly's Adventure
description: Move : →←↑↓ Jump : Space bar (You can long Jump or short Jump) Respawn : Space bar Reset the save point : R

name: TheBeanstalk
description: Jack reached the giant's castle in the sky riding the beanstalk that grew into the sky. But the gates were tightly shut...

name: Kidz Bop Dance Party!
description: Introducing Kidz Bop's first game, a puzzle that plays 10 of today's biggest hits! Personalize it to get the party started: Pick your level of play, choose your game avatar, find the right party background and even play DJ!

name: LeapSchool Reading
description: Meet the kids from the coolest school in the world in this fun reading adventure.

name: LeapSchool Math
description: Build your knowledge of mathematics as you help out the LeapSchool students. Explore weight and volume by mixing up special bubble bath potions. Learn about measurements, proportions and geometry when you make stuffed animals and create games Sell your creations to raise money to make repairs around LeapSchool.

name: Crazy Otto
description: Originally, Ms. Pac-Man started as an unauthorized hack of Pac-Man called Crazy Otto by General Computer Corporation, featuring a Pac-Man-like character with a blue eye and legs. To avoid another lawsuit with Atari (which they had previously received for creating "Super Missile Attack", a Missile Command hack), G.C.C. presented the game to Bally Midway for approval of release. Midway, impatient for Namco to release the then-upcoming Super Pac-Man, purchased Crazy Otto for their own release, transformed into Ms. Pac-Man.

name: Green Lantern
description: Green Lantern is a cancelled SNES platformer based on the DC Comics character of the same name.

name: Bitcoin Bounce
description: How far can you travel along the blockchain? Bounce your bitcoin along the blocks and try to land on the combo blocks to boost your score. The aim is to see how far you can get without landing on enemies or missing the blockchain and landing into oblivion!

name: Little Nemo and the Nightmare Fiends
description: Little Nemo and the Nightmare Fiends is a 2D non-linear platformer with 4 playable characters that players can freely switch between. The game features artwork inspired by the groundbreaking 1905 Little Nemo in Slumberland comic, hand-drawn keyframed animation, and a cast of surreal creatures and characters.

name: Lisa the Joyful: Growing Pains
description: LISA the Joyful: Growing Pains is a Lisa the Joyful mod/fan game in development focusing on breathing new life into the game while polishing pre-existing elements. New story beats, dialogue, and interactions!New areas, NPCs, and environments to explore! New artwork and gameplay to existing environments! A new optional party member! New battles, items, moves, and weapons! New music tracks!

name: Hero Youseijyo
description: Hero Youseijyo is an old style raising mini game. Train up a Hero to defeat the Demon King.

name: Blockhead 2D
description: Blockhead 2D is a mostly multiplayer, retro-style platformer. It comes with a cast of characters, game mechanics that resemble the classic 8-bit brawlers and sound design that keeps the action going!

name: Fortitude Invasion
description: The alien invasion has already begun! They're already here! Who can help the brave warriors to learn the full power of our civilization!?

name: Yippy Cube
description: Yippy Cube is a happy party game. You will incarnate cute animals, place and eliminate cubes falling from the sky with your friends in various interesting stages. Whether working together to achieve the goals or PK with other teams, you will have constant joy and fun.

name: TotalNerds
description: You play Jona & Louise in a city where everyone seems to have something to hide. People have secrets and a plot has been hatched. Who can you trust? Better to trust no one, not even technology.

name: Vein
description:
Game is currently in around the clock development and will include bugs and potential room for improvement

A hybrid of multiplayer and single player open-world post-apocalypse survival RPG set in the near future.

name: Rooftop Garden Simulator
description: Who said the city can’t be its own escape? In Rooftop Garden Simulator, you can transform your urban corner into a warm and relaxing agricultural space. Build, explore, and connect with the sprawling, citified landscape in a stylized simulation that’s designed to be fun for gamers of all ages.

name: Interruption
description: This is a text adventure game based on image selection. Players will explore the streets with girls after losing power. As time goes by, the reality will gradually blend into different scenery. You can't turn back. Your choice determines the direction you go.

name: Girls und Panzer: Atsumare! Minna no Sensha-dou
The Symphony of Dragon and Girls
Girls und Panzer: Senshamichi Dai Sakusen!
Fermata on the Pithos
description: Fermata on the Pithos is a third-person action adventure game where you control a small robot with one eye and a jet-pack in a near-future that has been hit by a catastrophic flood.

name: Spermination: Cream of the Crop
description: You may have beaten off others and came first a thousand times, but you've never tasted the sweet Cream of the Crop. This sequel is harder, faster and will blow your crusty socks off! Choose from 3 difficult leagues: Hand, Mouth and the coveted Cream Pie! Crack the egg & unlock your bundle of joy!

name: Brain Syndrome VR
description: Brain Syndrome VR is a FPS bullet hell shooter featuring a cell shaded art style and an option for local multiplayer. Even though the game has VR in the title, it can be played without it. The game has more than 12 hand crafted levels ready for you to explore.

name: House Haunting
description: House Haunting is a horizontal puzzle solving game. You need to solve puzzles in a haunted house. There is no fixed sequence for solving puzzles. You can freely explore the room, and finally complete the task "she" gave you, satisfy "their" wishes, and finally find "your" memory and destination.

name: Beat Shot
description: Dash and blast your way through rhythmically entranced enemies. Can you keep up with the beat?

name: Devils 'n Dragons Arcade
description: Devils 'n Dragons is a 2D run and fight platformer turned on arcade action in a medieval fantasy world.

name: Dad and Me: Super Daddy Punch Hero
Online @ The Perfect Time
description: With your exams coming up faster than you imagined, you needed to let off some steam and whilst waiting for take-out you stumbled on what seemed to be a new show. Soon enough you were diving head first into a new fandom. Will your heart be steady enough to embrace these new relationships or will the stress of it all cause you to make choices you wished to forget?

name: Hello Neighbor: Diaries
description: Some say he's a killer, that he hides kidnapped children in his basement. All you know is he's your Neighbor, and it's up to you to figure out what he's hiding.

name: Hassle Online
description: Hassle Online is an open world multiplayer action role-playing game with no limits, with thousands of players on one map. Join the criminal world of your native land and gather your gang of friends or take the side of the law and arrest the entire underworld!

name: Ocean: The Place in Your Heart
description:
Luna is a curious girl who loves adventure.
Join her on a journey to explore the mysterious abyss and make lots of various new friends.

name: My Success Story
description:
“My Success Story” is the most realistic life simulator game where you can get everything you miss in your real life. Simulation let you rise from rags to riches and get filthy rich. Start a family and run your own business in!

Is a dollar in your pocket and a room in the dorm all you have for now? Make choices to have a better life with work and family that you want! Try to become rich and successful business tycoon. Can you earn money to possess wealth and run your own business company? Check it out!

name: Mission Zero
description: Mission Zero is a 2v4 competitive stealth game featuring blend-in and distinguished gameplay experience.
